<br>
For my part, Sundays at the times of these Sidi raids, with also the relic raids seemingly an ongoing event now too, I have real life commitments and can't be here.  If I could, I would have Peckinpah logged on in Merlin waiting, cause as long as these boneheads schedule the raids at the same time every week I think we can count on a relic raid too.<br>
<br>
We aren't going to have the power relics for very much longer imo.  Hope the Sidi drops are worth it.<br>
